item.title: Astrology of the Chakras
item.description:
Astrology of the Chakras

It is well known to many of us by now that the "human energy field" is comprised of seven major energy centers or chakras that are located along the cerebral-spinal axis. Each of these centers acts as a substation or transformer of the universal energy or prana that flows through the medulla at the base of the skull.
